  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Several studies investigated the reproductive outcomes after surgical treatment of colorectal
      endometriosis, mainly segmental colorectal resection. Little information is available on the
      spontaneous fertility of patients with bowel endometriosis. This study aims to evaluate the
      fertility of patients affected by rectosigmoid endometriosis who did not undergo previous
      surgical treatment.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
